data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This beautiful one-level ranch-style house is a rare find in the most desirable neighborhood in the country. Situated on 2 perfectly level acres, this property is fully fenced and irrigated, ensuring privacy and convenience.Step inside and discover a meticulously updated interior with modern features and finishes that elevate both style and functionality. With many updates and newer features, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and charm.Enjoy the benefits of a great well and efficient flood irrigation system, providing abundant water supply for your needs. The presence of a barn adds versatility, making it ideal for hobbies, storage, or even equestrian pursuits.Located just on the edge of the city, you'll experience the best of both worlds - peaceful country living with easy access to urban amenities. Schools, shopping, and dining options are just a stone's throw away.Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional property.
